84
00:09:01,740 --> 00:09:02,811
Wait.

85
00:09:03,840 --> 00:09:04,911
Here.

86
00:09:06,281 --> 00:09:07,641
Don't get too nervous and good luck.

87
00:09:08,251 --> 00:09:09,281
Thanks.

88
00:09:13,620 --> 00:09:16,090
Here. Good luck to you too.

89
00:09:16,751 --> 00:09:17,891
Okay.

